@AdamWr I think it is because you have third party cookies disabled in the incognito session. I found that if I enable third party cookies in an incognito session, it appears to download just fine. 

![Screenshot 2024-04-23 193345](https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/assets/69532417/a3bbd9b9-9da9-4005-a5a4-20cc57105deb)
![Screenshot 2024-04-23 193449](https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/assets/69532417/d30170fa-9a43-4757-98cb-3123afd521e5)

@NUser2018 Вот такие проверьте (оба. Одно отключает старое):
```
octavius.mail.ru#@$#html.mobile .letter-list__react div.ReactVirtualized__Grid__innerScrollContainer { margin-top: -50px !important; }
octavius.mail.ru#$?#html.mobile .letter-list__react div.ReactVirtualized__Grid__innerScrollContainer { margin-top: 63px !important; }
```

Yes, it is more complicated. I'm not sure if the developers had time to study the scriptlets.
But can be used instead of the redirect rule.
